      <title>亞馬遜將無收銀購物技術推向更多第三方商店，同時退出</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amazon-push-cashierless-shopping-tech-into-more-third-party-stores-while-backing-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亞馬遜週三表示，計劃今年將其無收銀購物技術推廣到更多第三方商店，同時減少對自身技術的依賴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amazon-push-cashierless-shopping-tech-into-more-third-party-stores-while-backing-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
